🌸New Flavours / Promo Code🌸 Magi Planet is one of Taiwan’s leading gourmet popcorn brand which has made its presence in Singapore since 2012. They’ve been creating popcorn with Asian-inspired flavours and successful in doing so. Offering more than 20 MAGIcal and whimsical flavours like Corn Soup, Double Chocolate, Seaweed, to even Sizzling Mala. There will be plenty for you to savour and enjoy.
.

Love their Corn Soup flavour from their classic collection which has an intense corn flavour. This highly addictive treat is deliciously sweet and savoury all at once. They just came out with Two New Flavours under Thank you series. It is specially designed as a reward for yourself for bearing through this difficult period or as a token of appreciation to someone you are grateful to. 
1. Turmeric Curry with a healthy dose of turmeric, curry powder, onion and other savoury spices paired with pure longan nectar honey, this bright golden-colour popcorn exudes an exotic aroma and flavour of mustardy, spicy and peppery all combined. 
2. Garlic Butter a unique blend of natural garlic glove and garlic powder tossed with quality cheese powder from Brazil and New Zealand, this popcorn is specially baked to bring out the distinctive garlicky fragrant layered with rich buttery and cheesy taste. .

@magiplanetsg are hand-crafted using only the finest and freshest ingredients. These are definitely a perfect companion for Netflix nights. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
.
Promo Code: "EndCovid19" to get 19% discount

Available in limited quantities only at sg.magiplanet.com and Shopee https://shopee.sg/magiplanetsg
.
